{"id": "1442114420640583761", "channel_id": "1438621511081791538", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "或者生存能力真的很堪憂也能上鯊魚，不過鯊魚就要裝靈魂誕生/跨越疼痛", "timestamp": "2025-11-23T11:27:51.071000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438621511081791538", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "誕妄．墨菲機制與搭配探討", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1441260974085636297", "1174179716706619494"]}
